Summary: ipfw and dummynet for Linux
Name: %{name}
Version: %{version}
Release: %{release}
License: BSD
Group: System Environment/Kernel
Source0: %{name}-%{version}.tar.bz2
BuildRoot: %{_tmppath}/%{name}-%{version}-%{release}-buildroot

Vendor: unipi
Packager: PlanetLab <marta@onelab2.iet.unipi.it>
